  "body": "## Bug Report\r\n\r\n<!-- Thanks for your bug report! Don't worry if you can't fill out all the sections. -->\r\n\r\n\r\n### What version of TiKV are you using?\r\n<!-- You can run `tikv-server --version` -->\r\nmaster: 7c679639885172814c4ef28f00d190337ce284a4\r\n\r\n### What operating system and CPU are you using?\r\n<!-- If you're using Linux, you can run `cat /proc/cpuinfo` -->\r\nAWS i3.4xlarge\r\n\r\n### Steps to reproduce\r\n<!-- If possible, provide a recipe for reproducing the error. A complete runnable program is good. -->\r\nWe execute 'drop table' in a TiDB-cluster, and then import data to TiKV by TiLightning.\r\nThen I observer the size of block cache decreasing to 4GB from 64GB. \r\n\r\n### What did you expect?\r\nWe expect that the capacity of block-cache remain unchanged.\r\n### What did happened?\r\n![image](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/16376959/74008129-19df5480-49bb-11ea-8308-452e8aa14173.png)\r\n",
